<h3><a href="http://edgytech.com/umongo/" target="_blank">UMongo</a></h3>

<p>UMongo是一个基于Java的GUI应用程序，可以浏览和管理MongoDB的集群。它是可用于Linux，Windows和Mac OSX。</p>

<ul>
	<li>connect to a single server, a replica set, or a MongoS instance</li>
	<li>DB ops: create, drop, authenticate, command, eval, &hellip;</li>
	<li>Collection ops: create, rename, drop, find, insert, save, &hellip;</li>
	<li>Document ops: update, duplicate, remove, &hellip;</li>
	<li>Index ops: create, drop, &hellip;</li>
	<li>Shard ops: enable sharding, add shard, shard collection, &hellip;</li>
	<li>GUI Document builder</li>
	<li>Import / Export data from database to local files in JSON, BSON, CSV format.</li>
	<li>Support for query options and write concerns (getLastError)</li>
	<li>Display of numerous stats (server status, db stats, replication info, etc)</li>
	<li>Mongo tree refreshes to have a real time view of cluster (servers up/down, durability, etc)</li>
	<li>All operations are executed in background to keep UI responsive</li>
	<li>Background threads can repeat commands automatically</li>
	<li>GUI is identical on all OS</li>
</ul>

